===Noun===
'''septicemia'''

# {{pathology}} A disease caused by the presence of pathogenic organisms, especially [[bacterium|bacteria]], or their toxins, in the [[bloodstream]], characterised by chills and fever.

====Synonyms====
* [[blood poisoning]]
* [[septic fever]]

